	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Have you looked at the Famicom Game Repeater by Hori?  It looks pretty cool.  The trick to it seems to be that it uses a controlled pass-through for the system power.  If timed right, theoretically that should allow random number generators to be seeded in a repeatable way.

		

		</td>
